<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">近日，由我校退役军人教育学院制作的十二集动画视频集《江西省退役军人教育培训和就业创业政策解读微视频》被江西省退役军人事务厅采用。该系列视频选题精准、思路清晰、创作精美，在退役军人事务部培训中心</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">“强军网”适应性培训平台及“江西省退役军人事务厅”公众号、门户网站投放后取得了非常好的宣传效果，助推了我省退役军人教育培训和就业创业政策宣传工作步入了新领域。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32pt;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-18%2010%3A17%3A06%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%201.png?Expires=2020904226&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=V%2Br546FxY%2Ftwy3gfiDQhOlABhJk%3D" alt="" width="650" height="930" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p><br/></p>